# Semgrep ignore patterns — align with CodeQL exclusions in GitHub Actions
# Infra YAML / Helm charts / CRDs generate high-noise k8s-security findings;
# these are covered by dedicated manifest scanning (trivy-config, kubeaudit) not semgrep.

# Helm charts + CRDs
infra/charts/**
infra/**/templates/**
**/*.crd.yaml
**/crds/**

# Build / vendored / generated
target/
node_modules/
**/node_modules/**
dist/
build/
**/dist/**
**/build/**
.next/
**/.next/**
**/vendor/**

# Test fixtures and mocks
test/fixtures/**
tests/fixtures/**
**/__fixtures__/**
**/__mocks__/**
**/testdata/**

# Documentation and session artifacts
docs/
_runs/
intake/
memory/
archived/

# Package lockfiles (not source)
**/package-lock.json
**/yarn.lock
**/Cargo.lock
**/bun.lockb
**/deno.lock

# Generated assets
**/*.min.js
**/*.min.css
assets/
avatar/

# Git / tooling
.git/
.github/
.gitlab/
.cursor/
.claude/
.codex/
